Class LoggerDecorator

java.lang.Object
logger_decorator.LoggerDecorator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Logger
Direct Known Subclasses:
TimeLogger, UserDataLogger
public abstract class LoggerDecorator extends Object implements Logger
Decorator that allows for adding new functionalities to loggers without modifying their structure. This class serves as base for creating specific logger decorators.
